dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Dane County, WI 2025
dc_description_s: This data represents roads and Right of Ways (ROW) for Dane County, Wisconsin in 2025 and includes the layers 'DANE_ROADS_2025' and 'DANE_ROW_2025'. [Roads: This layer is a detailed line feature dataset of the Dane County roadway network containing attributes such as street name and address ranges, ZIP codes, speed limits and routing.Row: This dataset is a representation of the public road right-of-way in Dane County, Wisconsin. This feature does not represent ownership, but rather the right-of-way that may be publicly owned or an easement.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
